quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  23,105,"Wi'anee…ìe ka du…ó…óugol …ìe: "Enee, Aayeeje Alqur'aana …óen laatanooki no janngee e dow mo'on ka aduna, laati…óon hi…óon fenna …óe?!""
  23,106,"∆Åe wi'i: "Joomi amen, foolii men ko adii kon ka Ganndal Maa…óa immorde e malkiso amen, men woniino yim…ìe majju…ìe gaayi Goonga kan.""
  23,107,"Joomi amen, yaltin men ka Yiite, si men yiltitike faade e ko men wonnoo kon e mu'un immorde e keefeeru e majjere haray menen ko men too√±u…ìe wonkiiji amen, gom…óii nganto amen ngon ta∆¥ii."
  23,108,"Alla Daala: "Ho…óee ka nder Yiite ko on jaasu…ìe hoynaa…ìe, wata on haalanam [fii yaltineede]."
  23,109,"Pellet, laatinoke fedde e jeyaa…ìe Am …ìen, …ìen gom…óin…ìe Lam, hi…ìe wi'a: "Joomi amen, men gom…óinii Ma haforan men bakkatuuji amen …óin, Yurmiraa men Yurmeende Maa…óa nden, ko An ∆Åuri Mo∆¥∆¥ude Yurmetee…ìe …ìen."
  23,110,"Jogiti…óon …ìee gom…óin…ìe noddoo…ìe Joomi mu'un nokku fii jalkitugol hi…óo jalnora …ìe, jalnor…óon …ìe haa jalnorgol …ìe ngol yejjintini on ja≈ãtagol Alla, laati…óon hi…óon jala …ìe jalkita."
  23,111,"Min, Mi yo…ìirii …ìee gom…óin…ìe he…ìugol Aljanna on √ëalnde Darngal; fii mu√±al ma…ì…ìe ngal e dow …óoftagol Alla e dow ko …ìe laatinoo kon hi…ìe hawra e mu'un sabu mo'on immorde e lorra."
  23,112,"O Daali: "No foti heewde ko √±ii…ìu…óon ka leydi immorde e duu…ìi? No foti heewde ko yeebu…óon ton immorde e waqtu.""
  23,113,"∆Åe jaabora wi'ugol ma…ì…ìe: "Men √±ii…ìii √±allal maa…óum see…óa e √±allal, lanndo …ìen toppitii…ìe e limugol √±al…ói e lebbi.""
  23,114,"O Daali: "On √±ii…ìaali ka aduna si wanaa jamaanu hun fan…óu kun, no newii mu√±√±agol e nder makkun e dow …óoftaare sinndo onon on laatino hi…óon anndi emmbere √±ii…ìugol moo…óon."
  23,115,"Kaa on sikku -onon yim…ìe …ìen- wonndema ko Men Tagiri on ko fijindaaru gaanin √±ee√±al, hara mbarjaari alah Lepte alah yeru muumi(jawdi) …óin, hara onon on ruttetaake faade e Amen √ëalnde Darngal fii Hasboore nden e njo…ìdi ndin?!"
  23,116,"Alla Senike Lam…óo firlitotoo…óo e nder tagu Makko ngun ko O muuyi kon, On Mo Ka√±um ko O Goonga Konngol Makko ngol ko Goonga, rewetee…óo e goonga alah tanaa Makko, Jooma Arsi Tedduki kin, kin ki ka√±um no …ìuri mawnude tageefooji …óin, on mo laatii Jooma ko …ìuri mawnude kon e tageefooji …óin haray ko Kanko woni Jooma majji …ói fow majji."
  23,117,"On mo rewi wonndude e Alla rewetee…óo goo hara o maraa hujja jojji…óugol makko e dewal ngal (ko …óum woni fiyaake kala rewaa…óo tanaa Alla) anndu pellet, njo…ìdi golle makko bon…óe …óen no ka Joomi makko Senaande wonanii Mo, ko Kanko woni On yo…ìiray∆äo mo …óum Leptugol mo, pellet, Kanko O malnirtaa heefer…ìe …ìen he…ìugol ko …ìe …óa…ì…ìata kon, wanah da…óugol ko …ìe hulata kon."
  23,118,"Maaku -an Nulaa…óo-: "Joomam haforanam bakkatuuji am …óin, Yurminiraa mi Yurmeende Maa…óa nden ko An woni ∆Åur…óo Mo∆¥∆¥ude kala Yurmii…óo jom bakkaatu, ja…ìu tuubuubuyee am on.""